cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image denoising and evaluation of denoising algorithms. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the dataset contains uncompressed color images. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper introduces a method for estimating the true noise level in each image. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as one of the denoising algorithms analyzed is a Multi-Layer Perceptron. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possibility as the paper deals with image processing and manipulation.
